QuestData.Title: The Overwhelming Swarm
QuestData.Description: I command the sentinels of Niuzao. Every defender out there can hold his own against the mantid swarm.$b$bThe kunchong, however, are something different.$b$bThey are massive, violent, and without a question the biggest threat to my sentinels' lives. Only Niuzao stands a chance against them. Niuzao... and perhaps you.
